INSERT_WITH_FK: INSERT INTO users (id_country, gender, birthday, name, lastname, nickname, email) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
INSERT_WITHOUT_FK: INSERT INTO items (name, price, offer) values ($1, $2, $3)
UPDATE_WITH_FK: UPDATE devices SET name = $1 WHERE id = $2
UPDATE_WITHOUT_FK: UPDATE os SET name = $1 WHERE id = $2
GET_MORE_THAN_A_TABLE: SELECT os.name FROM sessions JOIN devices ON sessions.id_devices = devices.id JOIN os ON devices.id_os = os.id
GET_GROUP_ONE_TABLE: SELECT name, count(*) FROM items WHERE name ILIKE 'a%' GROUP BY name
GET_GROUP_MORE_THAN_A_TABLE: SELECT devices.name as "Device most used", count(*) FROM sessions JOIN devices ON sessions.id_devices = devices.id GROUP BY devices.id ORDER BY count(sessions.id_devices) DESC
